text: Gheorghe Popovici (born 4 May 1938) is a Romanian wrestler. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1938 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Romania Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Chișinău
title: Gheorghe Popovici (wrestler)
